{"tid":790500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB: 中美進一步互徵關稅 國家商務部稱要捍衛自身權益","createTime":"2018-08-23T05:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T00:24:30.000Z","uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b63d7698354971afd02f0edc0e1d3bc443275c89","tid":790500,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"講到大家關係對等咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰擴大，中美在本港時間中午起互相向對方總值160億美元貨品開徵關稅。國家商務部稱，為了捍衛自由貿易及自身權益，不得不繼續作出反擊。<br />\n<br />\n踏入美國東岸周四凌晨、即本港時間中午12時01分，美國針對中國的第二輪關稅措施生效，向總值160億美元中國產品加徵兩成半關稅，涵蓋工業製品、航空引擎零件等279項商品。<br />\n<br />\n中<span style=\"color: red;\">方表明會對等反制，向美國同等價值的333項商品加徵兩成半關稅，包括能源化工、汽車零件。<br />\n</span><br />\n美國傳媒報道，中方代表團當地周三到財政部出席中美貿易談判，是雙方官員超過兩個月以來首度接觸。會談為期兩天，聚焦解決中美貿易僵局。"},{"pid":"94db03fb5abf5831f24529bcacf2dee98267ebcc","tid":790500,"uid":28195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tvb-17_KeiGE_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftvb-17_KeiGE_1200x0.png&h=240ff3e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46c96f9d1a76be1e828ac99584dbb8f859870698","tid":790500,"uid":28195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"94db03fb5abf5831f24529bcacf2dee98267ebcc","tid":790500,"uid":28195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tvb-17_KeiGE_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftvb-17_KeiGE_1200x0.png&h=240ff3e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"TVB隸屬中共國務院，同三商中既生意模式一樣"},{"pid":"4eed4a2bb1406cc7d67a94b71df3d952cba5fa16","tid":790500,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"輸"},{"pid":"70a8017642ab6a4b79080c73e873a0d319dd42ac","tid":790500,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"55<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cabe22d34ff7f9cfda85f1d71e9ed3f2467e913","tid":790500,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T00:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0babc5f62b479952df8565de5c0987ff24acd0d9","tid":790500,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T00:24:30.000Z","msg":"自身=共產黨"}]}